  <brief_title>Effect of an Allergen Vaccine in Patients With Allergic Rhino-Conjunctivitis and Asthma Due to House Dust Mite Allergy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety, Immunogenicity and Clinical Efficacy of an Allergen Vaccine (AllQbG10) in Subjects With Allergic Rhino-Conjunctivitis and Asthma Due to House Dust Mite Allergy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
