  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to test the safety, tolerability, immunogenicity and clinical
      efficacy of the combination treatment AllQbG10 in patients with rhino-conjunctivitis and
      asthma due to house dust mite allergy in a single-center, open-label setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
